                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_2" name="SelInputRadio_1" value="2")
                            label(for="inputRadio_2" class="c-CheckSelected w100 col-flex ml10 mr10 mt20" ng-click="txtcaptura_a='up'") Pattern of work.

                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_3" name="SelInputRadio_1" value="3")
                            label(for="inputRadio_3" class="c-CheckSelected w100 col-flex ml10 mr10 mt20" ng-click="txtcaptura_a='up'") Move.
                        div(class="mb20 row-flex mt40")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  2. 
                                | The verb #[strong switch] off means:
                        div(class="mb20 row")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_4" name="SelInputRadio_2" value="1")
                            label(for="inputRadio_4" class="c-CheckSelected w100 col-flex ml10 mr10 mt20" ng-click="txtcaptura_a='down'") To start working.

