                        div(class="mb20 row")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_10" name="SelInputRadio_4" value="1")
                            label(for="inputRadio_10" class="c-CheckSelected w100 col-flex ml10 mr10 mt20" ng-click="txtcaptura_a='down'") To travel by plane.

                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_11" name="SelInputRadio_4" value="2")
                            label(for="inputRadio_11" class="c-CheckSelected w100 col-flex ml10 mr10 mt20" ng-click="txtcaptura_a='up'") The feeling of being very tired and sometimes confused because you have travelled on a plane across parts of the world where the time is different.

                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_12" name="SelInputRadio_4" value="3")
